{"id":"errors/NG0507","title":"NG0507: 服务器端渲染后 HTML 内容被修改","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n\n  <h1 id=\"ng0507-html-content-was-altered-after-server-side-rendering\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"exhgo1drwks5j7wencgbrb5h1\">NG0507: 服务器端渲染后 HTML 内容被修改<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG0507#ng0507-html-content-was-altered-after-server-side-rendering\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n  \n  \n\n  <div class=\"error-description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG0507#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3sv8mf31m91khwxnf6mnlnzyy\">当Angular检测到服务器端渲染（SSR）生成的内容在渲染后被更改时，将引发此错误。水合过程依赖于在SSR后内容保持不变，其中包括空格和注释节点。这些空格和注释节点必须在SSR过程生成的HTML中保留。在\n<a href=\"guide/hydration#constraints\">水合指南</a>中了解更多信息。</p>\n\n  </div>\n\n\n  \n  <br>\n\n  <div class=\"debugging\">\n    <h2 id=\"debugging-the-error\">如何排除本错误<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG0507#debugging-the-error\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9suv0130vftmw2dfsxdapnru8\">通常发生在以下情况下：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4lk8jmxnyw93qt4wuoh0mhd8d\">一些CDN提供商内置了删除HTML中空格和注释节点的功能作为优化选项。请验证CDN配置中是否有这样的选项，并将其关闭。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5jix7lmhufmcpf14ysz3i3ww1\">如果您对SSR生成的HTML进行自定义后处理（作为构建步骤），请确保此过程不会删除空格和注释节点。</li>\n</ul>\n\n  </div>\n  \n</div>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - errors\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - errors/NG0507#debugging-the-error\n - errors/NG0507#description\n - errors/NG0507#ng0507-html-content-was-altered-after-server-side-rendering\n - guide/hydration#constraints\n-->"}